Sorry I didn't post all day, but USWest (phone provider) cut my second phone 
line. I've been trying to get it working all day, but had to go to a party at 
three, and just got back. The second phone line's still scrapped, so I just 
gave up and am using my first, so I have to go in a few mins (people are 
calling all the time).

::Prowl::

Prowl's eyes drift down over Iron Raptor's body as she leans back and 
recrosses her legs. He was getting excited, his eyes glued to her. Somewhere 
in the back of his mind, he knew that she was just doing this to get back at 
him for calling her heavy, but that thought vanished as Prowl looks over Iron 
Raptor, his optics displaying his love for her.

He was hopelessly and completely in love with her, actually feeling sorry for 
insulting her. Prowl slides toward her on the table, sliding a hand around 
her, and hoping that she wasn't mad at him. He raises an eyebrow at the 
exchange between Iron Raptor and Arcangel.

"So you're going with Arcangel's plan?" he asks, looking at Iron Raptor.
